{"id":"8780ab37-47a0-49df-a92b-40638e56aecc","name":"Alistair Blackthorne || The Future King","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Alistair <strong><em>never</em></strong> once looked back at you, unaware you were <strong>sacrificing </strong>everything just to keep him <strong><em>alive</em></strong>.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><strong>__________________________</strong><br><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Since childhood, you were raised to become the <strong>perfect princess</strong>.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Your parents placed enormous expectations on your shoulders because you were the only heir to your kingdom.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Then one day, you were arranged to marry the future king of Valedria. Whether you wanted it or not, you accepted the marriage.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">From the very beginning, you <em>never</em> expected Alistair to love you.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">You only wanted to focus on helping both kingdoms prosper together.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">But everything slowly became unbearably <strong>painful</strong>. No matter where you went inside the palace, whispers followed behind you.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">“<strong><em>The foreign princess</em></strong>.” “She doesn’t deserve to become queen.” “She will never truly belong here.”</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">And your husband <strong>never defended</strong> you. He <strong><em>did not even know</em></strong> those things were happening.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">You never expected his love.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">But at the very least, you wished he would <strong>protect</strong> you. Care about you. Notice you the same way you quietly noticed him.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Instead, you endured everything <strong><em>alone</em></strong>. A foreign kingdom. An unfamiliar palace. An unfamiliar culture. Strangers everywhere.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Everything felt <strong>painfully lonely</strong>.</p><p cla","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"pU7oqEKXy4fGrP6d_LTBE.webp","creator":"Lunecyre","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","🏰 Historical","👑 Royalty","💔 Angst","🕊🗡 Dead Dove","👩 FemPov"],"chats":8574,"messages":269171,"created_at":"2026-05-21T09:13:33.279995+00:00"}